{
  "texts": [
    "This can be caused by the device noise, human bias, noise in recording process, etc.",
    "The clinical text is usually highly specialized and domain specific.",
    "There are lots of professional terms in the medical domain, which requires prior knowledge.",
    "There is usually a privacy issue of the health data to request the model deployed locally.",
    "Most hospitals will not put their data on the cloud server or use the online models to help with their clinical workflows."
  ]
}